h quality hardware the facility permits the manufacture of intricate detail parts from raw material sheet rod forge blank mixtures etc through complex final assembly and cleaning processes for more than half a century we have developed innovative products to support our customer’s needs around the world now as we pave the way for the next generation we continue to build on our global status in the market place and set ever higher standards to continually exceed customer and employee expectations arrowhead products copyright    all rights reserved   arrowhead products  history arrowhead products was founded in  as arrowhead rubber company in  arrowhead rubber conceived the idea of rubber coated fabric ducting which gave birth to airtron products this rapidly became the company’s most important product during wwii in  arrowhead rubber company was sold to national motor bearing in  arrowhead rubber began designing and producing highaltitude pressure suits called gus garment upper stratosphere the suit was also worn by hollywood actor lee marvin in a movie titled man in orbit in  federal mogul purchased national motor bearing and changed the name of the company from arrowhead rubber company to arrowhead products in  the company moved from its signal hill location to los alamitos and in  being a pioneer in the space industry arrowhead products was awarded the prime contract from nasa to design and manufacture the entire propellant system first stage apollo booster rocket in  arrowhead products was sold to vesper corporation now called industrial manufacturing company based out of brecksville oh our legacy continues for future generations arrowhead products copyright    all rights reserved   arrowhead products  manufacturing arrowheads products specializes in the manufacture of complex metallic and structural composite systems and components using titanium inconel cres nimonic and other unique exotic alloys and materials that include carbon fiber kevlar and other laminates we provide the very best in machining welding forming heat treatment sheering laser machining curing autoclave and ovens assembly and all necessary ndt processes all under one roof arrowhead’s products have been aboard almost every aircraft and spacecraft in the past half century the company’s advanced capabilities have earned it global recognition and an impressive list of customers in the commercial aviation defense and space markets arrowhead’s primary goal is to offer the most reliable products and the most responsive service to its customers by providing superior design with the assurance of quality and on time delivery arrowhead products’ manufacturing success is based on decades of experience utilization of proprietary manufacturing techniques and its continuous improvement efforts through s kaizen lean and sixsigma principles our capabilities range but are not limited to cnc tube bending cnc routers vacuum and atmosphere furnace orbital welding cnc lathe welding laser machining waterjet machining gerber cutting autoclaves bellows forming machines stake welding resistance seam welding short run assembly weld fixtures hydroforming up to  ton forming press machines complete machine shop complete tool and die shop master model and plaster shop   arrowhead products copyright    all rights reserved   arrowhead products  support arrowhead products’ fluid distribution systems fds ducts and components are engineered to provide innovative solutions to distribute high and low fluid volumes at various temperature ranges through a variety of complex systems bleed air system ducting environmental control ecs thermal antiice tai exhaust duct for apu auxiliary power unit cryogenic propellant lines missile and space applications arrowhead products copyright    all rights reserved   arrowhead products  support  introduction arrowhead products offers repairs of its products through its faa part  certificated repair facility located on the premises our repair station number is ohtrx we are also easa approved turnaround time ranges from  to  days after receipt of quote approval and may occasionally vary depending on availability of certain subcomponents  warranty arrowhead products offers a warranty to the original equipment purchaser of any products that it is free from defects in workmanship and materials for a period of  years on new product warranty does not cover wear and tear associated with normal operations during the warranty period arrowhead products allows warranty returns to the factory for repair or replacement of any part which is in nonconformance to its specifications if you are not sure the part is warrantable please contact a customer service representative to get answers to your questions prior to shipping doing so will prevent delays at receiving and expedite your orders and claims once a part is received arrowhead products will either accept or deny warranty based on initial testing and inspection of the part down to the component level customerinduced damage resulting from misuse mishandling missing components or modification to such parts is considered a nonwarrantable condition and therefore warranty will be denied refurbishment or upgrading of a product to the latest specification is considered nonwarranty and will be reconfigured to a repair service transaction arrowhead products is not responsible for any damage to the product during transportation to our facility please insure that parts are properly packaged for their journey to arrowhead arrowhead products rigorously tests all its products to ensure optimum quality and reliability however in the event of a failure return the part to arrowhead products for evaluation and testing if warranty is accepted the customer will be notified of the acceptance and arrowhead will repair the unit or replace at its option at no cost to the customer further warranty repairs will be returned to customer freight prepaid if after evaluation and testing the customer’s reason for removal or failure symptom can not duplicated unit passes test it will be reported as “no fault found” nff and a bench test fee of  will apply if warranty is accepted on a returned part any replaced or repaired subcomponent will carry a ninety  day warranty or the remainder of the initial factory warranty period whichever is longer  repair and overhaul ro for nonwarranty repairs or services arrowhead products offers a wide range of repair solutions for those components which may require minor refurbishment on up to major damage correction after receiving inspection arrowhead products will examine the returned parts and send customer a quote for the repairs repair work will only commence on the part when a signed quote approval or a purchaserepair order has been received  evaluation fees arrowhead products standard bench testevaluation fee is  this fee will apply to transactions determined to be no fault found nff or that the unit is outside of repairable limits or deemed beyond economical repair ber parts may be returned in “as is” condition with no work performed or they may be scrapped on site per customer’s written request parts returned to customer for either of the instances mentioned in this paragraph will be shipped at customer freight expense arrowhead products at its discretion may decide not to repair a nonwarranty part  expedite and aog repairsarrowhead products offers expedite services for critically needed parts for an additional charge please contact a customer service representative for more information to avoid delays be sure to have on hand all pertinent information including part number mfr date condition and detailed information as to the reason for removal or squawk  insulated products evaluation notice please note certain arrowhead parts require the careful removal of the outer insulationcovering in order to evaluate test to arrive at a quotation for customers please note that once it is removed the material is discarded and cannot be salvaged or reapplied this operation is a standard part of the evaluation process as the insulation material can not be retained on the part after testing therefore instances where insulated products are returned at the customers request without actual repair work work performed may or may not have the original insulation material intact  shipping ship repair and overhaul parts to arrowhead products attn ro receiving dept  katella avenue los alamitos ca   contact us you can reach us at our phone or fax numbers or you can fill out the form below and we will contact you phone fax name name is required company name company is required email email is required   invalid email format telephone telephone is required   invalid telephone format message message is required  char max             arrowhead products copyright    all rights reserved   arrowhead products llc  new orleans la  company information products resources my account talk to a db advisor  business directory la new orleans aircraft parts and equipment nec aircraft parts and equipment nec arrowhead products llc a arrowhead products llc claim this business  industrial ave new orleans la  get directions business info founded  incorporated annual revenue  employee count  industries aircraft parts and equipment nec contacts contact business your email address subject message send message company summary arrowhead products llc was founded in  and is located at  industrial ave in new orleans it employs  employees and is generating approximately  in annual revenue verified status unverified address unverified last verified  phone unverified payment method unverified view full report similar businesses nearby our similar businesses nearby shows similar businesses in their industry and region based on information found in their dun  bradstreet credibility review profile competitive landscape our competitive landscape shows how this business compares to similar businesses in their industry and region based on information found